description: Experience the best of South Boston city living in this beautifully updated 1 bedroom condo with top-tier amenities. Featuring an updated kitchen with gas cooking, a cozy gas fireplace, and a modern bath, this unit offers both style and comfort. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry, central air, and ample closet space for effortless living.  Step outside to your private covered deck, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. With assigned parking you’ll never have to worry about finding a spot. Nestled in a prime South Boston location, you’ll have easy access to restaurants, shops, public transportation, and the waterfront.  Don’t miss your chance to own a piece of city living at its finest!
